description:
I remuxed this with AC3 audio instead of AAC like the other upload here which was created 

with some unknown program. My Blu-Ray won't play aac and possibly others wil not either so 

here is a file that has been tested on a Samsung BR player. It is a few MB larger because 

AC3 has a larger footprint than AAC.
